@endnode

@node future "RxTD Guide - Future"

    I`m going to start developing RxTD2 but I`ll leave RxTD around and maybe do some
  bug fixes but I`m not adding anymore features.

  For RxTD bug fixes see @{"problems" link problems} section

  RxTD2 initial release features
    · Support for left-out icons
    · No spaces in paths problems
    · Handles multiple selected files
    · Supports multiple commands per item
    · Menu creation script 5-7 times faster than RxTD's

  RxTD2 future features
    · Prefs editor (ReAction GUI based on ToolsPrefs)
    · Hotkeys
    · Add MENU type (to CLI & WB) so user menu items can combine built-in menu cmds


@endnode

